     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CodeSystem encounter-businessstatus-inpatient</b></p><a name=\"encounter-businessstatus-inpatient\"> </a><a name=\"hcencounter-businessstatus-inpatient\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Last updated: 2025-10-29T00:00:00Z</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profile: <a href=\"shareablecodesystem.html\">Shareable CodeSystem</a></p></div><p>This case-sensitive code system <code>http://hl7.org/fhir/encounter-businessstatus-inpatient</code> defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">pre-admit<a name=\"encounter-businessstatus-inpatient-pre-admit\"> </a></td><td>Pre-admit</td><td>The patient has been pre-admitted but has not yet arrived at the facility.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">pend-admit<a name=\"encounter-businessstatus-inpatient-pend-admit\"> </a></td><td>Pending Admit</td><td>The patient admission is pending.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">admit<a name=\"encounter-businessstatus-inpatient-admit\"> </a></td><td>Admitted</td><td>The patient has been admitted to the facility.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">discharge<a name=\"encounter-businessstatus-inpatient-discharge\"> </a></td><td>Discharge</td><td>The patient is in the process of being discharged or has been discharged.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">unknown<a name=\"encounter-businessstatus-inpatient-unknown\"> </a></td><td>Unknown</td><td>The inpatient business status is unknown. Note that \"unknown\" is a value of last resort and every attempt should be made to provide a meaningful value other than \"unknown\".</td></tr></table></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
